Usage: createSignalPin [-help] [-ignore_floating_pins] {-inst <instList> | -pins <pinLinst>}

-help                     # Prints out the command usage
-ignore_floating_pins     # ignore floating pins (bool, optional)
-inst <instList>          # name list of insts (string list, required)
-pins <pinLinst>          # name list of pins ((instTerm)+, optional)